<p><strong><font color = "#C00000"Size 5>Getting MADD......</strong></font></p>

<p>Mothers Against Drunk Driving (MADD) has administered a &#8220;call to action&#8221; plan for the youth of America. Recently, they changed their mission statement to incorporate the prevention of underage drinking. The new statement reads as follows: &#8220;The mission of MADD is to stop drunk driving, support the victims of this violent crime, and prevent underage drinking.&#8221;</p>

<p>MADD would like the assistance of the AAU Family in making this &#8220;call&#8221; a reality.  MADD is asking organizations like the AAU to step up and speak to the young people about the dangers of both underage drinking and drinking and driving.  </p>

<p>With the holidays full of parties just around the corner, the message of PLAY IT SAFE &#8211; &#8220;Don&#8217;t Drink and DRIVE&#8221; needs to be driven home.  If you would like more information about MADD, please visit <A HREF:"http://www.madd.org">www.madd.org. </A></p> 

